### Admin: POST request to create a new employee, returns 200, has authority and CsrfToken
POST http://localhost:8080/management/api/v1/employees
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic admin admin
X-XSRF-TOKEN: ef7a2e95-7237-4675-bc5f-d5b27b31c76c

{
  "employeeId": "7f3a8c1e-9d2b-4b6a-8c7d-ef0123456789",
  "employeePosition": "Senior Developer",
  "firstName": "Micheal",
  "lastName": "Jordan",
  "email": "mj@me.com",
  "password": "michealJ123"
}

